A U.S. Navy engineer breaks silence about a forbidden flight path over Antarctica. What he and his crew witnessed near the South Pole defied explanation — a vast structure beneath the ice, a vanishing science team, and warnings that came without paperwork.

In this cinematic breakdown, we explore one of the most mysterious testimonies connected to Earth’s most remote continent. Was it just a medevac gone wrong — or a glimpse into something we weren’t meant to see?
